name: sae-architecture-integration
description: Use when adding a new SAE architecture family in sparsify-ascend, or when a run fails with Unknown architecture, missing factory dispatch, or other architecture-registration issues. This skill gives a repo-specific checklist for wiring new sparse coder families into sparsify/config.py and sparsify/sparse_coder.py, plus the exact smoke-validation sequence to run before declaring the family runnable.
